<p align="center">腾格里挑战赛（专业组）正在进行</p>
<p align="center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201009/8d9b68b6c39e4ecb8c79a657e43415d6.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
